  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "2. In a bowl, mix together mansaf, smoked egg, middle eastern spices, and pine nuts.",
    "3. Drizzle eastern-style olive oil over the mixture and toss to coat.",
    "4. Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "5. Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and bake for 20-25 minutes, or until heated through.",
    "6. Garnish with fresh parsley and serve hot."
